It is a plant reaching tall, with spiky flowers, yellow with the filaments of stamens purple and densely hairy. The leaves are petiolate, dark green, slightly hairy. The stem is angular.
Data based on : Julve, Ph., 1998 ff. - Baseflor. Index of botanical, ecological and chorologique of the flora of France. Version : April 23, 2004.
